<paragraph blockId="136.[151,1436,152,978]" pageId="136" pageNumber="137">
DERIVATION OF SPECIFIC EPITHET: The name 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Borkent" authorityYear="2008" box="[826,883,912,937]" class="Insecta" family="Corethrellidae" genus="Corethrella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="136" pageNumber="137" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hirta">
